New-patches: sacha@free.net.ph--main/emacs-wiki--sacha--1.0--patch-69
Summary: With a prefix, planner-create-task-from-buffer prompts for a plan page. Also, planner-rss has category note.
Keywords: 

	* planner.el (planner-create-task-from-info): Pay attention to
	plan and date.
	(planner-create-task-from-buffer): With a prefix, prompt for a
	plan page. If a plan page is specified and this is not equal to
	the current annotation, move annotation into the task
	description.
	(planner-read-non-date-page): New defun.
	(planner-create-task): Add plan-page.

	* planner-rss.el (planner-rss-add-note): Add category link.
